### Design Notes for the Deck
- Keep the palette consistent with the dashboard and report: deep green (#0F5E4E), emerald (#10B981), and blue (#3B82F6) accents on a white/light background.
- Reuse the three charts already generated for the written report (revenue donut, KPI growth bars, roadmap timeline) rather than recreating new ones — this keeps visual continuity between the report, the dashboard, and the deck.
- Keep each slide to a maximum of 3–4 bullet points on-screen; the fuller talking points above are for the spoken narration, not the slide text itself.
